I"^<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/sysctl.d/20-disable-ipv6.conf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.lo.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.eth0.disable_ipv6 = 1
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Activate changes:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sysctl <span class="nt">-p</span> /etc/sysctl.d/20-disable-ipv6.conf
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

